'''Samsung Galaxy Camera'''是一个[[傻瓜相机|傻瓜相机]]，是一个基于Android的移动设备。Galaxy Camera在2012年8月宣布的口号是“相机。重生。”（{{lang-en|Camera. Reborn.}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.samsung.com/sg/promotions/galaxycamera/|title=Samsung GALAXY Camera|publisher=Samsung Electronics|date=|accessdate=2012-09-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120919001059/http://www.samsung.com/sg/promotions/galaxycamera/|archivedate=2012-09-19}}</ref>，但当时没有提及的价格或出货日期。<ref>[http://www.dpreview.com/news/2012/08/29/Samsung-Galaxy-Camera Samsung's Android-powered Galaxy Camera: the most connected camera?] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/2012/08/29/Samsung-Galaxy-Camera |date=20130709121526 }} DP Review, 2012 Aug 29</ref>

该相机采用16万像素的CMOS传感器和21倍的光学[[变焦镜头|变焦镜头]]，以及[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]和[[3G|3G]]连接，一个{{link-en|GPS接收器|GPS navigation device}}，可以在照片上标记[[地理标记的照片|地理位置]]。相机附带的软件可以存储，组织，编辑和在线共享图像和视频<ref>{{cite web |author=Samsung Galaxy Camera review |url=http://www.androidcentral.com/samsung-galaxy-camera-review |title=Samsung Galaxy Camera review |publisher=Android Central |date= |accessdate=2013-01-09 |archive-date=2013-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130107084544/http://www.androidcentral.com/samsung-galaxy-camera-review |dead-url=no }}</ref>。与其他Android设备一样，其他软件可以从[[Google_Play|Google Play]]等商店下载。<ref>[http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/20/technology/personaltech/androidcameras-from-nikon-and-samsung-go-beyond-cellphones-review.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 Android Cameras from Nikon and Samsung] {{Wayback|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/12/20/technology/personaltech/androidcameras-from-nikon-and-samsung-go-beyond-cellphones-review.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0 |date=20121223081408 }} by David Pogue, NY Times, Dec 20, 2012</ref>


